Step by step process-
----------------------------------------

1) Set up Emails in .env
2) Set up DB in .env
3) Create & write code in User_verification migration
4) Add "is_email_verified" field on fillable array in User model and create new model call UserVerify
5) Create Auth\AuthController
6) Create Route
7) Write Codes in AuthController
8) Migrate to DB
9) Create IsVerify Middleware
10) Write code on Middleware
11) Set up Middleware in Karnel
12) Set up & Write Codes on Views